SUMMARY:Bite-Size Charity for MAKE Roanoke at Vinton Pizza Hut!
DESCRIPTION:MAKE Roanoke\nMAKE Roanoke is hosting a fundraiser at the Vint
 on Pizza Hut on Tuesday\, March 10 from 10 AM - 11 PM!\n\nReady for a mout
 hwatering meal that supports a great cause? Join us at Pizza Hut (1060 Byp
 ass Road) on Tuesday\, March 10th between 12:00 AM - 11:30 PM and make a d
 ifference! With every order you place\, 20% will be donated to MAKE Roanok
 e. Be sure to [show this flyer](https://drive.google.com/file/d/18XU4S1E32
 MnQMEU4qqjjUnTM79NRbEru/view?usp=drive_link) to have your purchase count t
 owards our fundraiser!\n\nMAKE Roanoke has made just shy of $800 thanks to
  restaurant charity fundraisers like this one. We appreciate your support!
 !
